<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="send-vt">send <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /send/    美 /send/  </p>
<p>(sent, sent)</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>邮寄；发送：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>send a letter / an email 
寄信/发电子邮件</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>send sb sth / send sth to sb</strong>:
</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We sent her a letter of apology. / We sent a letter of apology to her. 
我们给她寄了一封道歉信。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>打发；派 (人)：</strong></h4>
<ul>
<li>send sb to some place / on sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He has to send Mary to hospital. 
他不得不送玛丽去医院。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The company sent her on a training course. 
公司派她去参加一个培训课程。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Luckily she was not badly injured and we sent her to the nearest hospital.
幸运的是，她受伤不重，我们将她送往最近的医院。</p><footer>2014 湖北书面表达改</footer></div>

<ul>
<li>send sb / sth to do sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The National Park Service had to send water trucks to provide water for the visitors. 
国家公园管理局不得不派水车为游客供水。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>传达；转告：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Advertising <strong>sends</strong> the <strong>message</strong> that you have to be thin to be successful. 
广告传递的信息是，要想成功就得瘦。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="send-away">send away</h3>
<p>1.<strong>解雇；把…打发走：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He was sent away by his boss. 
他被老板解雇了。</p></div>

<h3 id="send-for">send for</h3>
<p>1.<strong>派人去叫；召唤：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Her mother was ill, so she sent for a doctor. 
她母亲病了，于是她派人去请了一位医生来。</p></div>

<h3 id="send-out">send out</h3>
<p>1.<strong>发出 (光、味、声音等)；送出；派遣：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The sun sends out light and heat. 
太阳发出光和热。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Thousands of technicians have been sent out of the country to learn modern technology. 
成千上万的技术人员被派出国去学习现代技术。</p></div>

<h3 id="send-up">send up</h3>
<p>1.<strong>发出；射出；长出：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>When did China send up its first man-made satellite?
中国是在什么时候发射了自己的第一颗人造卫星？</p></div></div>